{"id": "1522520247444177048", "channel_id": "1522520247444177048", "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "content": "感谢各位守密人的支持！《忘却前夜》新OST已发布，欢迎收听、下载及分享。\n如果有基于OST的二次创作，也欢迎分享给我们！二创请遵照同人规则，OST内容请勿商用。\n\n**忘却前夜OST：命定同织之戏**\n帷幕起落，戏目更迭，她仍在剧院之中——她是剧作家，观众，亦是演员。\n命运的女主人啊，你如此残忍，永远缄默，却又为何而垂泪？    \n\n✦ 致敬：G.F. Händel - \"Lascia ch'io pianga\" \n✦ 音乐改编/制作：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\n✦ 企划：B.I.A.V. Studio\n\n——✦——✦—— ✦✦✦ ——✦——✦——\n\nThank you for your support!\n\nMorimens new OST was released today. Welcome everyone to listen, download and share.\nIf you have secondary creations based on the OST, please also share them with us!\n (Please follow the rules of the fandom for secondary creations, and do not use the OST content for commercial purposes)\n\n**Morimens OST: Play of Interwoven Fates**\nCurtains rise and fall, programs change, yet she remains within the theatre—playwright, audience, and actress all at once.\nO Mistress of Fate, so cruel and ever silent—for whom, then, do your tears fall?    \n\n✦ Original Composition: \"Lascia ch'io pianga\" by G.F. Handel\n✦ Arrangement & Adaptation: F.R.K. / B.I.A.V. Studio\n✦ Produced by: B.I.A.V. Studio\n✦ Planning: B.I.A.V. Studio", "timestamp": "2026-07-03T08:31:54.049000+00:00", "pinned": true, "thread_id": "1522520247444177048", "reactions": [{"emoji": "🔥", "emoji_id": null, "count": 10}, {"emoji": "Arachne_Spooder", "emoji_id": "1507430213787582628", "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1522520247641313373", "filename": "0a293874acc64ac0.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 490308, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1522520247444177048/1522520247641313373/0a293874acc64ac0.png?ex=6a48c4fa&is=6a47737a&hm=1655d3b94f90d14b92e2664d4873bd4fe70c3e46f534563b83432ce5aa101201&"}]}
{"id": "1522520323998879836", "channel_id": "1522520247444177048", "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "content": "**01. 幕起二重唱-Opening Duet**\n幕布拉开，荒唐的角色轮番登场。\n他们高歌，她们舞蹈，在命运堕临之前，执着地将戏码呈上舞台，即使结局早已写就。\n\nThe curtain parts, and absurd characters take the stage in turn.\nThey sing, they dance, and ere fate descends, they steadfastly bring their drama to the boards—though the ending has long since been written.", "timestamp": "2026-07-03T08:32:12.301000+00:00", "thread_id": "1522520247444177048", "edited_timestamp": "2026-07-03T08:32:19.276000+00:00", "attachments": [{"id": "1522520323210219530", "filename": "01._-Opening_Duet.wav", "content_type": "audio/wav", "size": 32258112, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1522520247444177048/1522520323210219530/01._-Opening_Duet.wav?ex=6a48c50c&is=6a47738c&hm=8e37b7b6cbe62bf956434a5c18f2e086c46f5accbb7c6d8bb8e0e4d3845a0277&"}]}
{"id": "1522520329912717362", "channel_id": "1522520247444177048", "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "content": "", "timestamp": "2026-07-03T08:32:13.711000+00:00", "type": 6, "thread_id": "1522520247444177048", "reply_to": "1522520247444177048"}
{"id": "1522520447571202119", "channel_id": "1522520247444177048", "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "content": "**02. 阿多尼斯-Adonis**\n少许苦精，20ml甜味美思，一些雪莉酒，加满冰块搅匀——这是一杯上好的开胃酒，也是一场上演了五百次的戏。\nA dash of bitters, 20ml of sweet vermouth, a measure of sherry, brimming with ice and stirred—a fine aperitif indeed, and a play performed five hundred times over.", "timestamp": "2026-07-03T08:32:41.763000+00:00", "thread_id": "1522520247444177048", "attachments": [{"id": "1522520447059628105", "filename": "02._-Adonis.wav", "content_type": "audio/wav", "size": 28728486, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1522520247444177048/1522520447059628105/02._-Adonis.wav?ex=6a48c529&is=6a4773a9&hm=8d8de88c5ac5b3cd1a4c0d2f856a7a0bb6d1b65ddd5960d4468025f5d37e9ad1&"}]}
{"id": "1522520494740344833", "channel_id": "1522520247444177048", "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "content": "**03. 微醺舞会-The Tipsy Ball**\n亲爱的，让我们借着酒兴，再共舞一曲吧。\nMy dear, let us, in our wine-warmed mirth, share one more dance.", "timestamp": "2026-07-03T08:32:53.009000+00:00", "thread_id": "1522520247444177048", "reactions": [{"emoji": "🔥", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1522520494794997840", "filename": "03._-The_Tipsy_Ball.wav", "content_type": "audio/wav", "size": 42271656, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1522520247444177048/1522520494794997840/03._-The_Tipsy_Ball.wav?ex=6a48c535&is=6a4773b5&hm=04b5363249cf4b0e4b35d86d90d8fe42f026af2bf4705d495ae56a65e4cfba16&"}]}
{"id": "1522520530283003974", "channel_id": "1522520247444177048", "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "content": "**04. 众生之线-Threads of the Living**\n那些行于世间，无比真实、看似自由的面孔，不过是舞台上的固定装置。\n一举一动，皆被命运的丝线牵引。\n\nThose faces that walk the world—so real, so seemingly free—are but fixed properties upon the stage.\nTheir every gesture is drawn along by the threads of fate.", "timestamp": "2026-07-03T08:33:01.483000+00:00", "thread_id": "1522520247444177048", "attachments": [{"id": "1522520530018766858", "filename": "04._-Threads_of_the_Living.wav", "content_type": "audio/wav", "size": 28835340, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1522520247444177048/1522520530018766858/04._-Threads_of_the_Living.wav?ex=6a48c53d&is=6a4773bd&hm=4cebaa6aab0903bad7e14b6b82f1e5fc7356367da182d84d28f5cccd7ae8b47b&"}]}
{"id": "1522520605168111686", "channel_id": "1522520247444177048", "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "content": "**05. 揭开她的面纱-Unveil Her**\n弦乐徐起，侍女吟唱。\n幕后之人来到台前，她向你行礼，邀你见证这既定的命轨。\n\nThe strings rise softly; the handmaiden lifts her voice.\nShe who dwelt behind the curtain steps forth to the front, bowing to you, inviting you to bear witness to this predestined orbit of fate.", "timestamp": "2026-07-03T08:33:19.337000+00:00", "thread_id": "1522520247444177048", "attachments": [{"id": "1522520604811591720", "filename": "05._-Unveil_Her.wav", "content_type": "audio/wav", "size": 25656270, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1522520247444177048/1522520604811591720/05._-Unveil_Her.wav?ex=6a48c54f&is=6a4773cf&hm=9c6c97a5a02a25f225aece2822634fe35c59b944ff1262551b9a48d73c38ebb1&"}]}
{"id": "1522520777872642078", "channel_id": "1522520247444177048", "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "content": "**06. 被遗弃的「我」-The Forsaken \"I\"**\n为了让一切位于正轨，总有事物该被剔除，被摒弃。\n未被选中的存在，尽数坠入漆黑的深渊，它们的哀嚎与咒骂，终究无人听见。\n\nThat all may keep its proper course, certain things must be excised, cast aside.\nThe unchosen tumble, one and all, into a pitch-black abyss—their wails and curses heard by none.", "timestamp": "2026-07-03T08:34:00.513000+00:00", "thread_id": "1522520247444177048", "attachments": [{"id": "1522520777516388382", "filename": "06._-The_Forsaken_I.wav", "content_type": "audio/wav", "size": 24349188, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1522520247444177048/1522520777516388382/06._-The_Forsaken_I.wav?ex=6a48c578&is=6a4773f8&hm=7152f77febda22c43736cafa264f20980ca9f8bcd2e0b4529dfee1e8e59a75dc&"}]}
{"id": "1522520936451018883", "channel_id": "1522520247444177048", "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "content": "**07. 蝴蝶振翅时-A Butterfly's Wingbeat**\n世人喜欢将一场战争归咎于一声枪响。\n但命运会嗤笑，这是全人类的自欺欺人。\n\nThe world loves to lay the blame for war upon a single gunshot.\nBut fate only sneers—such is the self-deception of all mankind.", "timestamp": "2026-07-03T08:34:38.321000+00:00", "thread_id": "1522520247444177048", "reactions": [{"emoji": "🔥", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1522520936153219204", "filename": "07._-A_Butterflys_Wingbeat.wav", "content_type": "audio/wav", "size": 53060580, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1522520247444177048/1522520936153219204/07._-A_Butterflys_Wingbeat.wav?ex=6a48c59e&is=6a47741e&hm=d7fc25e583fc832685495d5b044f4c38af320d77efd92a6c1c650c522b4883d9&"}]}
{"id": "1522521009289297953", "channel_id": "1522520247444177048", "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "content": "**08. 战火的前序-Prelude to War**\n不过是一名狂热青年，在一个寻常的街角开了枪。\n至少在那时，所有人都这样想。\n\nMerely a fervent youth, firing a shot upon some ordinary street corner.\nSo, at least, did everyone believe at the time.", "timestamp": "2026-07-03T08:34:55.687000+00:00", "thread_id": "1522520247444177048", "reactions": [{"emoji": "🔥", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1522521009285238814", "filename": "08._-Prelude_to_War.wav", "content_type": "audio/wav", "size": 33919650, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1522520247444177048/1522521009285238814/08._-Prelude_to_War.wav?ex=6a48c5af&is=6a47742f&hm=26a57ed7ea41696d5d4acdc76715e8f9db8b86b96f4a67e6ccca70d306524c7e&"}]}
{"id": "1522521100678860920", "channel_id": "1522520247444177048", "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "content": "**09. 世界复本-Replica World**\n世界给予你无数可选的岔路，但它们汇于同一点——名为毁灭，名为终焉。\nThe world offers you countless branching paths, yet all converge upon a single point—called ruin, called the end.", "timestamp": "2026-07-03T08:35:17.476000+00:00", "thread_id": "1522520247444177048", "edited_timestamp": "2026-07-03T08:35:33.834000+00:00", "attachments": [{"id": "1522521100087459890", "filename": "09._-Replica_World.wav", "content_type": "audio/wav", "size": 51177498, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1522520247444177048/1522521100087459890/09._-Replica_World.wav?ex=6a48c5c5&is=6a477445&hm=7aac8e092aad37428f810457dde8e7ac8a3d96476e999771b2195ad1d1979403&"}]}
{"id": "1522521134623621220", "channel_id": "1522520247444177048", "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "content": "**10. 将定之事，已定之事-What Was, What Shall Be**\n笔尖在白纸上飞奔，追逐着文字，而文字通往早已定好的结局。\n一切，都发生在你翻开每一本书之前。\n\nThe pen's tip races across the white page, chasing after the words, and the words lead to an ending long since determined.\nAll of it transpired before ever you opened the book.", "timestamp": "2026-07-03T08:35:25.569000+00:00", "thread_id": "1522520247444177048", "edited_timestamp": "2026-07-03T08:35:40.105000+00:00", "attachments": [{"id": "1522521134342471821", "filename": "10._-What_Was_What_Shall_Be.wav", "content_type": "audio/wav", "size": 63694422, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1522520247444177048/1522521134342471821/10._-What_Was_What_Shall_Be.wav?ex=6a48c5cd&is=6a47744d&hm=36deb82c4ec0c7bf8dca5c5b95e8a8020d731ee27ea84687df12e221d379b439&"}]}
{"id": "1522521363703795724", "channel_id": "1522520247444177048", "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "content": "**11. 舞剧：《天鹅之死》-Ballet: Le Cygne**\n这是一生仅能表演一次的即兴舞蹈。\n但没关系，它将有幸成为标本，永远定格。\n\nThis is an improvised dance one may perform but once in a lifetime.\nNo matter—it shall have the honor of becoming a specimen, frozen forever in place.", "timestamp": "2026-07-03T08:36:20.186000+00:00", "thread_id": "1522520247444177048", "attachments": [{"id": "1522521363414257785", "filename": "11._-Ballet_Le_Cygne.wav", "content_type": "audio/wav", "size": 16974564, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1522520247444177048/1522521363414257785/11._-Ballet_Le_Cygne.wav?ex=6a48c604&is=6a477484&hm=23a41d98eecc5d58ac26cf100dd6fcacdbabdec4e4334f23ec57459e86fd00bd&"}]}
{"id": "1522522245354881065", "channel_id": "1522520247444177048", "author_id": "231543819026300928", "author_name": "crowlov1", "content": "Jokes on you I already listened it on YouTube music", "timestamp": "2026-07-03T08:39:50.388000+00:00", "thread_id": "1522520247444177048", "reactions": [{"emoji": "Brown_think", "emoji_id": "1459080117308620996", "count": 1}]}
{"id": "1522525237495861308", "channel_id": "1522520247444177048", "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "content": "**12. 至美的抵偿-Recompense of Beauty**\n这样死去，真美。她想。\nTo die like this—how beautiful, she thought.", "timestamp": "2026-07-03T08:51:43.770000+00:00", "thread_id": "1522520247444177048", "attachments": [{"id": "1522525237026230272", "filename": "12._-Recompense_of_Beauty.wav", "content_type": "audio/wav", "size": 104878422, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1522520247444177048/1522525237026230272/12._-Recompense_of_Beauty.wav?ex=6a48c99f&is=6a47781f&hm=bcebc814137e93d000f069d4e2df7711da7130ff62721a78bb23e4b82ec47d55&"}]}
{"id": "1522525313131614319", "channel_id": "1522520247444177048", "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "content": "**13. 独角戏-Monodrama**\n他们共同歌唱，他们各司其职。\n但他们都是她。\n这是属于她的永不落幕的独角戏。\n\nThey sing in chorus; each plays their part.\nYet all of them are her.\nThis is her own monodrama, where the curtain shall never fall.", "timestamp": "2026-07-03T08:52:01.803000+00:00", "thread_id": "1522520247444177048", "attachments": [{"id": "1522525312838139924", "filename": "13._-Monodrama.wav", "content_type": "audio/wav", "size": 69646296, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1522520247444177048/1522525312838139924/13._-Monodrama.wav?ex=6a48c9b1&is=6a477831&hm=a5076d0b960cd84a41b1dd194a06e8ce34aadf5447ee699164c22f23fc7dcb85&"}]}
{"id": "1522525338528383097", "channel_id": "1522520247444177048", "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "content": "**14. 无尽螺旋-Endless Spiral**\n快过来吧，快过来吧，所有人都在等你。\n行过漫长的回廊，踏上永恒的舞台。\n你可是整部戏，唯一的主角呀。\n\nCome now, come now—everyone awaits you.\nWalk the long corridor, ascend the eternal stage.\nYou are, after all, the sole protagonist of the entire play.", "timestamp": "2026-07-03T08:52:07.858000+00:00", "thread_id": "1522520247444177048", "attachments": [{"id": "1522525338251427963", "filename": "14._-Endless_Spiral.wav", "content_type": "audio/wav", "size": 51908574, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1522520247444177048/1522525338251427963/14._-Endless_Spiral.wav?ex=6a48c9b7&is=6a477837&hm=df391f00a0a76b3790f56d04764951ec63aa44884ab48badd8ec863652237eb8&"}]}
{"id": "1522525402109575278", "channel_id": "1522520247444177048", "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "content": "**15. 渎命演出-Sacrilege in Performance**\n倘若毁灭终究无法避免，是否扯破命运的网，才能迎来真正的救赎？\n没有人能回答，没有神能够回答。\n但至少，无边的苦难也会一并消亡。\n\nIf ruin cannot in the end be averted, must one tear asunder the net of fate to find true salvation?\nNo mortal can answer; no god can answer.\nBut at least, the boundless suffering shall perish along with it.", "timestamp": "2026-07-03T08:52:23.017000+00:00", "thread_id": "1522520247444177048", "attachments": [{"id": "1522525401782550558", "filename": "15._-Sacrilege_in_Performance.wav", "content_type": "audio/wav", "size": 18858390, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1522520247444177048/1522525401782550558/15._-Sacrilege_in_Performance.wav?ex=6a48c9c6&is=6a477846&hm=bb01dea7862e4de7cfcd590038f0bbab2fdf6428ea64631bd1e5a9f910524f1a&"}]}
{"id": "1522525608268005376", "channel_id": "1522520247444177048", "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "content": "**16. 纺春的幻梦-Spring-Spinner's Reverie**\n梦醒过后，一切都会消失，被彻底忘却——庄园、花圃、歌谣、画作......\n那是一个不存在的春天。\n\nWhen the dream ends, all shall vanish, utterly forgotten—the manor, the flower garden, the songs, the paintings...\nIt was a spring that never was.", "timestamp": "2026-07-03T08:53:12.169000+00:00", "thread_id": "1522520247444177048", "attachments": [{"id": "1522525607907561562", "filename": "16._-Spring-Spinners_Reverie.wav", "content_type": "audio/wav", "size": 56981808, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1522520247444177048/1522525607907561562/16._-Spring-Spinners_Reverie.wav?ex=6a48c9f8&is=6a477878&hm=05d3334a5e978ff5bc8052ee325e84cc9abda4b1f58e359e11fbcae01177b22f&"}]}
{"id": "1522525758386339852", "channel_id": "1522520247444177048", "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "content": "**17. 三幕戏-A Play in Three Acts**\nAct I:纺丝\nAct II:衡量\nAct III:裁断\n如此往复，如此往复......\n\nAct I: The Spinning\nAct II: The Measuring\nAct III: The Cutting\nThus it goes, thus it goes, again and again...", "timestamp": "2026-07-03T08:53:47.960000+00:00", "thread_id": "1522520247444177048", "attachments": [{"id": "1522525758407442534", "filename": "17._-A_Play_in_Three_Acts.wav", "content_type": "audio/wav", "size": 61966428, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1522520247444177048/1522525758407442534/17._-A_Play_in_Three_Acts.wav?ex=6a48ca1b&is=6a47789b&hm=dc4c5a56f36bd2ef316f17f8fb8a55399d01c97defd3dea54fe9d3771a017f8b&"}]}
{"id": "1522525993686798427", "channel_id": "1522520247444177048", "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "content": "**18. 弄臣莅临-The Jester Arrives**\n你把命运当作丑角，便不会被命运奴役。\n用永不止歇的大笑来迎接祂吧，让我们共同唤出祂的名讳——\n欢愉。\n\nTreat fate as a clown, and you shall not be enslaved by it.\nGreet Them with laughter that never ceases—let us call out Their name together—\nRapture.", "timestamp": "2026-07-03T08:54:44.060000+00:00", "thread_id": "1522520247444177048", "attachments": [{"id": "1522525993368289392", "filename": "18._-The_Jester_Arrives.wav", "content_type": "audio/wav", "size": 104631442, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1522520247444177048/1522525993368289392/18._-The_Jester_Arrives.wav?ex=6a48ca53&is=6a4778d3&hm=e35e298bf0c48ad913782e771e58d1941bb34a1e97c245f9dca1021c2b40e310&"}]}
{"id": "1522526074934792193", "channel_id": "1522520247444177048", "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "content": "**19. 复仇鬼的悲歌-Avenger's Lament**\n“我恨你，恨你作茧自缚，恨你无能为力，恨你抛弃自己。”\n“......可这份仇恨也在灼烧我自己，因为，我也爱你。”\n\nI hate you—hate you for spinning your own cocoon, hate you for your helplessness, hate you for forsaking yourself.\n\"...Yet this hatred sears me as well, for I love you, too.\"", "timestamp": "2026-07-03T08:55:03.431000+00:00", "thread_id": "1522520247444177048", "attachments": [{"id": "1522526074896908349", "filename": "19._-Avengers_Lament.wav", "content_type": "audio/wav", "size": 21956580, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1522520247444177048/1522526074896908349/19._-Avengers_Lament.wav?ex=6a48ca67&is=6a4778e7&hm=38022a416acad8d3397260787651997852cbeaac0fb10fe07738adf92a9dcfce&"}]}
{"id": "1522526296108695553", "channel_id": "1522520247444177048", "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "content": "**20. 命运啊，你何其残酷-Mia Cruda Sorte**\n吱呀，吱呀。\n命运啊，你的轮盘转动不歇。\n贫穷与权力都被你像冰一般消融。\n你遮蔽自己，又隐藏面目，\n却也向我闪耀......\n\nCreak, creak.\nO Fate, your wheel turns without rest.\\nPoverty and power alike you melt away like ice.\nYou veil yourself, and hide your countenance,\\nyet still you shine upon me...", "timestamp": "2026-07-03T08:55:56.163000+00:00", "thread_id": "1522520247444177048", "attachments": [{"id": "1522526295815225374", "filename": "20._-Mia_Cruda_Sorte.wav", "content_type": "audio/wav", "size": 42825498, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1522520247444177048/1522526295815225374/20._-Mia_Cruda_Sorte.wav?ex=6a48ca9c&is=6a47791c&hm=e9f4407e99ad599802b3d3d31516b13ad4bd89d2f6ae1081c9543f68943ab470&"}]}
{"id": "1522526912348553316", "channel_id": "1522520247444177048", "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "content": "**21. 共织终局-Finale, Interwoven**\n丧钟已然敲响，背弃者呈上最疯狂的演出。\n无数的丝线，将会织就什么样的结局——\n由你决定。\n\nThe death knell has tolled; the betrayers offer up their maddest performance yet.\nWhat ending shall these countless threads weave together—\nthat, you shall decide.", "timestamp": "2026-07-03T08:58:23.086000+00:00", "thread_id": "1522520247444177048", "attachments": [{"id": "1522526912033984672", "filename": "21._-Finale_Interwoven.wav", "content_type": "audio/wav", "size": 209469864, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1522520247444177048/1522526912033984672/21._-Finale_Interwoven.wav?ex=6a48cb2f&is=6a4779af&hm=94fbf944ec5bfe38c908419499a4ff4ae9b826d003784b70f87f4d58e096fed1&"}]}
{"id": "1522526933995356230", "channel_id": "1522520247444177048", "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "content": "**22. 囚徒正谢幕-The Prisoner Bows**\n观众为分别落泪，亦为重逢落泪。\n而舞台中央的犯人们，也该为她们彼此献上掌声。\n\nThe audience weeps at parting, and weeps again at reunion.\nAnd the prisoners at center stage shall, at last, give one another their applause.", "timestamp": "2026-07-03T08:58:28.247000+00:00", "thread_id": "1522520247444177048", "attachments": [{"id": "1522526933739376700", "filename": "22._-The_Prisoner_Bows.wav", "content_type": "audio/wav", "size": 61434732, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1522520247444177048/1522526933739376700/22._-The_Prisoner_Bows.wav?ex=6a48cb34&is=6a4779b4&hm=be2826d4bd9aeae4d362ab66c1ab240ea276ac2b3bd0ef0a26eb4f662f1745ca&"}]}
{"id": "1522527125218000988", "channel_id": "1522520247444177048", "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "content": "**23. 返场变奏-Encore: Variations**\n没有后日谈的演出是不完整的。\n稍稍改动台词，调整布景，轮换演员——每一次返场，都是崭新的一幕。\n\nA performance without an epilogue is incomplete.\nA slight alteration to the lines, an adjustment of the scenery, a rotation of the cast—every encore is a brand-new act.", "timestamp": "2026-07-03T08:59:13.838000+00:00", "thread_id": "1522520247444177048", "attachments": [{"id": "1522527124815085579", "filename": "23._-Encore_Variations.wav", "content_type": "audio/wav", "size": 46831848, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1522520247444177048/1522527124815085579/23._-Encore_Variations.wav?ex=6a48cb61&is=6a4779e1&hm=3d64cb6dc6b12aa0b4bbafa520c87767f4ca4c11661e61940a326babab7aa37e&"}]}
{"id": "1522527150828421151", "channel_id": "1522520247444177048", "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "content": "**24. 而我仍在歌唱-And Still I Sing**\n再会吧，在最后的旋律中。\n再会吧，在命运的注视下。\n故事的主人公，将踏上新的旅程。\n\nFarewell, in the final melody.\nFarewell, beneath the gaze of fate.\nThe protagonists of the story shall set forth upon a new journey.", "timestamp": "2026-07-03T08:59:19.944000+00:00", "thread_id": "1522520247444177048", "attachments": [{"id": "1522527150526300260", "filename": "24._-And_Still_I_Sing.wav", "content_type": "audio/wav", "size": 39091386, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1522520247444177048/1522527150526300260/24._-And_Still_I_Sing.wav?ex=6a48cb67&is=6a4779e7&hm=e8e904570b83815dc2b442ab7f0a94b607cb3d3b749b59afa59a84b59f639741&"}]}
